            <title>[LUDOC-169] Document the large_xattr option to tune2fs and mkfs.lustre.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-169</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Need to document the large_xattr option to tune2fs and mkfs.lustre.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#8220;tune2fs &#8211;O large_xattr &amp;lt;device&amp;gt;&#8221; is a valid command/argument. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#8220;--mkfsoptions=&apos;-O large_xattr&apos; &#8220; parameter to mkfs.lustre works. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
